o How to install

  1. Unfold the tar file.

    Example) $ cd /usr/local/src
             $ gzip -cd OZ++-R5.tar.gz | tar xf -

  2. You'll find a directory named OZ++-R5 and a file named INSTALL in the
     directory.  Follow the instructions written in INSTALL.


o How to operate OZ++ system

OZ++ system should be operated properly by operators understanding the contents
of the file doc/README.site.
